BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:Come join us for the Baltimore Indie Game Devs potluck picnic at BIG member Allen Lambert's house in Marriottsville just west of Baltimore. This picnic is for all local game devs in the Baltimore-Washington area. Allen will be manning the grill\, and there will be outdoor games as well as tabletop games to play.\n\nIf you'd like to bring something to the potluck\, please add it in the Comments section.\n\nNotes:\n\n• This is a NO ALCOHOL event.\n• In the event of rain\, we may postpone this event.\n• We'll send the street address to RSVP'd attendees one week before the picnic and the day before the picnic. Please send a message to Allen Lambert or Tony Li if you'd like the address sooner.\n\nEvent Link: https://www.meetup.com/baltimore-indie-game-developers-group/events/307582133/
DTEND:20250621T210000Z
LOCATION:Crows Foot Road\, Crows Foot Rd\, Maryland\, MD us
DTSTART:20250621T160000Z
