BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a delicious celebration of Bitcoin Pizza Day\, brought to you by PizzaDAO! 🍕💸\n\nOn this historic day\, we honor the legendary first real-world Bitcoin transaction: when Laszlo Hanyecz paid 10\,000 BTC for two pizzas in 2010. That single cheesy exchange ignited a worldwide movement and earned a permanent slice in crypto history!\n\nJoin us for a delicious celebration of Bitcoin Pizza Day\, brought to you by PizzaDAO! 🍕💸\nOn this historic day\, we honor the legendary first real-world Bitcoin transaction: when Laszlo Hanyecz paid 10\,000 BTC for two pizzas in 2010. That single cheesy exchange ignited a worldwide movement and earned a permanent slice in crypto history!\n🔥 What to Expect:\n✅ Casual networking – Meet fellow crypto enthusiasts\, builders\, and investors.\n✅ DeFi Demo – Presentation by local web3 developer who has built up $5 million in TVL\n✅ Good vibes\, great beer – No pitches\, no panels\, just fun and great conversation over drinks.\n🚗 Heads up: Parking is street parking only\, so plan accordingly!\n\nEvent Link: https://www.meetup.com/baltimore-cryptomondays/events/307624661/
DTEND:20250523T003000Z
LOCATION:Joe Benny's\, 313 S High St\, Baltimore\, MD US
DTSTART:20250522T223000Z
SUMMARY:Bitcoin Pizza Day Party with PizzaDAO
UID:2bc6488e-6ae6-4bfa-88bf-e1f11f113627@2bc6.org
